1
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:35,980
♪Looking at the bright lights
of the long streets in my hometown♪

2
00:00:36,260 --> 00:00:39,480
♪I wrote down
that it's not too late to meet you♪

3
00:00:39,780 --> 00:00:45,260
♪Rereading it now,
I think it's just a joke in life♪

4
00:00:46,540 --> 00:00:49,580
♪During my beautiful youth,
I longed for peace♪

5
00:00:49,740 --> 00:00:53,240
♪I vowed to face challenges with you
before Buddha♪

6
00:00:53,940 --> 00:00:59,380
♪I pray to the gods not to be alone♪

7
00:00:59,940 --> 00:01:03,140
♪Singing about farewell at Yang Pass♪

8
00:01:03,340 --> 00:01:06,300
♪Behind the sad song,
no one knows how I feel♪

9
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:13,100
♪Even though the streets are bustling,
I can only watch alone♪

10
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:16,500
♪Spend years on the sea,
drifting through foreign lands♪

11
00:01:16,780 --> 00:01:20,580
♪There have been
reunions and separations♪

12
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:26,300
♪There are countless sceneries,
none of them are half as good as you♪

13
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:30,180
♪I asked heaven and earth
where we can share the bright moon♪

14
00:01:30,420 --> 00:01:33,340
♪Looking back,
only the wind understands♪

15
00:01:33,660 --> 00:01:39,980
♪Turns out that when love is deep,
right and wrong are forgotten♪

16
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:43,500
♪Let me ask you
how black hair turns white?♪

17
00:01:43,820 --> 00:01:47,180
♪I answer myself,
saying it's been a long separation♪

18
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:53,980
♪In the blink of an eye,
I lost my youthful appearance♪

19
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:04,680
=Cao Xuanxuan's Love Journey=

20
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:07,220
=Episode 5=

21
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:09,140
(Lyu Residence)

22
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:10,240
This is mutton soup,

23
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,540
a local specialty of ours.

24
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:12,920
Please

25
00:02:13,020 --> 00:02:13,520
try it out.

26
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:15,560
It looks delicious.

27
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:16,080
Try it.

28
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:17,720
Oh, Mr. Zhao.

29
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,100
sorry for not greeting you.

30
00:02:19,100 --> 00:02:19,640
Forgive me.

31
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:20,440
Have a seat.

32
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,360
What brings you here?

33
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,160
Magistrate Guo?

34
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,000
Do you know each other?

35
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:27,040
Greetings, sir.

36
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:29,240
Are you at Mr. Lyu's residence
for the banquet as well?

37
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:29,760
Yes.

38
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,480
Bufan is my close friend for many years.

39
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,400
I simply had to come.

40
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:33,400
Yes, indeed.

41
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:34,360
Come on.

42
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,640
Everyone, let's enjoy the meal.

43
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,180
Eat before the food gets cold.

44
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:42,160
It's delicious.

45
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:42,680
Master!

46
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:43,880
Master.

47
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,080
What's the matter?

48
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:50,520
What is it?

49
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:53,440
No one saw Luo Ji all night.

50
00:02:53,820 --> 00:02:56,180
He didn't respond even
when the servant knocked at his door.

51
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:56,920
That's right.

52
00:02:57,060 --> 00:02:58,560
I went to look for him this morning.

53
00:02:58,780 --> 00:02:59,680
But no one responded.

54
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,080
That can't be.

55
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:02,760
This won't do.

56
00:03:02,940 --> 00:03:04,300
I need to go and check on him.

57
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,200
Excuse me,

58
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:06,280
everyone.

59
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,280
Let's go.

60
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:10,160
Let's follow him.

61
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,120
How many times did you knock?

62
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:12,800
Several times.

63
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:13,800
But no one answered.

64
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,640
Zijie,

65
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:17,580
do you think something happened

66
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:19,400
because of us again?

67
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:21,120
Then...

68
00:03:21,220 --> 00:03:22,320
Should we go check it out?

69
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,280
Let's go.

70
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,280
Let's check it out.

71
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:28,280
Sir, please enjoy your meal.

72
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,320
Hey, wait for me.

73
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,160
What's the matter?

74
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:38,960
Luo,

75
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,680
you died in such a tragic manner.

76
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:51,840
He's...

77
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:57,960
Was

78
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:59,200
the door locked just now?

79
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:00,520
How did you enter the room?

80
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,440
The door's latched from the inside.

81
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:03,960
I had to break in by force.

82
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:06,640
Just as I thought.

83
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,420
It's another locked-room murder.

84
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,040
Locked-room?

85
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:12,760
The audacity

86
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,680
to commit murder in broad daylight.

87
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:17,040
(Another locked-room murder?)

88
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,120
(Is it the same person?)

89
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:21,440
Miss,

90
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:22,600
what are you doing?

91
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:26,600
Luo had a special relationship
with Lord Su.

92
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:27,760
This is a serious matter.

93
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:30,300
Imperial Envoy has plenty
of experience handling cases.

94
00:04:30,340 --> 00:04:31,080
It's fine to leave

95
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:32,180
this case to him.

96
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:33,600
Yes.

97
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,320
Based on a coroner's technique,

98
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,120
it is possible to determine

99
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:04,000
the exact time of death accurately

100
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:06,360
by observing the condition
of the middle finger and the palm

101
00:05:06,420 --> 00:05:07,800
at different hours.

102
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,200
Based on this technique

103
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:10,520
and the stiffness of Luo's corpse,

104
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,960
he was killed last night

105
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,360
during the Chou hour.

106
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,120
Someone.

107
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:25,380
You all stay here and guard the scene.

108
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,920
Once we have everything figured out,

109
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,120
we'll handle Luo's body

110
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,560
properly.

111
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:32,800
Yes, sir.

112
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:46,280
No one is allowed

113
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,680
to leave until the investigation
is complete.

114
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,120
Mr. Zhao, do you suspect

115
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,360
that the person who killed Luo

116
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,880
is one of us?

117
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,880
What a joke.

118
00:05:58,040 --> 00:06:00,040
I'm working for the emperor.

119
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:02,400
If I am delayed from getting back,

120
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:05,000
can you take responsibility for it?

121
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,840
No use talking about that now.

122
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,640
Let's start

123
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:10,720
by checking everyone's alibis.

124
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:12,640
At the hour of Chou last night,

125
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:14,880
who were you with,

126
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,880
where were you at,

127
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:17,900
and who can confirm your whereabouts?

128
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,680
I was already asleep by midnight.

129
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,600
De can vouch for me.

130
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,520
Last night,

131
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,080
I felt stuffy indoors

132
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:27,560
and went out for a walk.

133
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,880
The night watchman can confirm it.

134
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:33,000
But Zheng,

135
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:35,200
you weren't in the room

136
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:36,880
when I returned.

137
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:45,440
I was with Mr. Zheng last night.

138
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:54,160
You young ones sure
have a lot of energy.

139
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,000
So, where were the rest

140
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,000
of you last night?

141
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:02,240
We were all together,

142
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,940
and we can vouch for each other.

143
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:05,320
Magistrate Guo and the others

144
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,480
were under my care last night.

145
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,640
I can vouch for them.

146
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,080
Mr. Zhao,

147
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,560
may I ask

148
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,640
where you were

149
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,040
last night?

150
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,280
Last night,

151
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,720
I couldn't hold my drinks.

152
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,400
So I went out for some fresh air

153
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,200
without informing anyone.

154
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,720
In that case,

155
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,760
no one has seen you, Mr. Zhao?

156
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:27,780
That's right.

157
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,200
Sir.

158
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:50,560
Mr. Zhao,

159
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:52,760
may I ask

160
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:54,600
what is that on the corner
of your clothes?

161
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:07,480
Mr. Zhao,

162
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:08,280
what...

163
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,600
Why is there blood

164
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,220
on your clothes?

165
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,320
I see.

166
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,680
No wonder no one can vouch for you.

167
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:17,000
Looks like the pot calling
the kettle black.

168
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:18,700
I just remembered something.

169
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,840
You and Luo Ji

170
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:21,200
had some issues, right?

171
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:25,120
Eunuch Wang,

172
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,600
don't make

173
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,240
wild accusations

174
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,200
in public like this.

175
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,840
We only have

176
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:31,960
a difference of opinion.

177
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,200
But his death

178
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,120
has nothing to do with me.

179
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:40,920
We can't judge a person
just by their appearance.

180
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,600
You're the prime suspect now.

181
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,000
I don't trust you

182
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,640
to solve this case.

183
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:49,960
All right.

184
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:52,640
To prove my innocence,

185
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:53,960
I am willing

186
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,720
to lock myself in a room

187
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,920
and stay there

188
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,360
until the case

189
00:08:58,520 --> 00:08:59,720
is solved.

190
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,720
Then

191
00:09:01,940 --> 00:09:03,420
we'll have to trouble you, Mr. Zhao.

192
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:04,840
All right.

193
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,640
Bufan,

194
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:10,480
once the case is fully investigated,

195
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,600
you can release me.

196
00:09:27,540 --> 00:09:28,320
Magistrate Guo,

197
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:31,100
my family has been crafting iron tools
for the court for generations.

198
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:33,380
This lock is our family heirloom,
an unbreakable lock.

199
00:09:33,420 --> 00:09:34,680
Everyone can rest assured.

200
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:35,960
But

201
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,720
Mr. Zhao is confining himself
in his room

202
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,640
to avoid suspicion.

203
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,260
Magistrate Guo,

204
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,880
as the Country Magistrate of Yan City,

205
00:09:43,020 --> 00:09:44,740
it's your duty to investigate this case.

206
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:46,000
What do you think?

207
00:09:48,980 --> 00:09:49,640
Magistrate Guo?

208
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,280
Given what's happened,

209
00:09:52,460 --> 00:09:54,140
I am obligated to take responsibility.

210
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,360
However, I'll need your help

211
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,240
with one thing.

212
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,280
No one is allowed to leave

213
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,520
until the case is solved.

214
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,720
Magistrate Guo, rest assured.

215
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:01,800
Without your permission,

216
00:10:01,820 --> 00:10:03,440
no one can leave Lyu Residence.

217
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,880
I appreciate your cooperation.

218
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:05,540
It's my duty.

219
00:10:05,981 --> 00:10:08,440
(Lyu Residence)

220
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,280
Come and take a look.

221
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:09,880
What is it?

222
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:11,390
I thought you were familiar with this.

223
00:10:11,420 --> 00:10:12,580
See if there are any clues.

224
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,520
Since you're asking me,

225
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,640
I'll take a look.

226
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,040
Xuanxuan,

227
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:30,640
this room is completely enclosed.

228
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,320
How did the killer enter

229
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:33,960
and how did he leave

230
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,160
after killing Luo Ji?

231
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,080
What if the killer

232
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,640
never entered this room at all?

233
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,040
How?

234
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,720
I once read a novel

235
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:44,000
where

236
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:45,680
the killer used

237
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,720
a crane

238
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:49,720
to lift the victim's bed

239
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:50,760
through a skylight

240
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,360
while

241
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:53,600
they were sleeping.

242
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:56,360
The killer decapitated the victim first.

243
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:57,880
Then he placed the bed

244
00:10:58,280 --> 00:10:59,360
in its original place.

245
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:00,800
The killer

246
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:01,760
never even

247
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:04,440
entered the room.

248
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:06,360
I understand

249
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:07,520
what she said.

250
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:09,000
But what is a crane?

251
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:12,280
It is the rolling equipment
you use in this time.

252
00:11:13,060 --> 00:11:14,200
I see what you're saying.

253
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:16,400
Are you saying

254
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:18,840
the killer first used some kind of tool

255
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:21,480
to shoot the candlestick like an arrow

256
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:24,360
and then used rolling equipment

257
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,960
to flip the body tied with a rope?

258
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:27,760
Clever.

259
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:28,680
That's how it happened.

260
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:32,240
But as it stands,

261
00:11:32,560 --> 00:11:33,600
this room

262
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,560
doesn't have a skylight.

263
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,040
That's right.

264
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,440
Miss He Chun,

265
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:42,920
you're a skilled martial artist

266
00:11:42,980 --> 00:11:44,040
and know leaping skills.

267
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:45,240
Can you go up and check?

268
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:47,280
Sure.

269
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:48,960
Be careful.

270
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,600
We'll watch from down here.

271
00:11:58,520 --> 00:11:59,160
Be careful.

272
00:12:01,820 --> 00:12:02,740
There's none, right?

273
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:05,160
Could there

274
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,480
be a hidden one?

275
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:08,160
Come on down.

276
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:29,720
We've checked.

277
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:37,800
There's no skylight.

278
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:38,720
There's none.

279
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:44,780
Come on. Let's go.

280
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:52,880
You, thug.

281
00:12:56,700 --> 00:12:57,800
So there's no skylight.

282
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,640
He's only a child.

283
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:24,680
Why not let him go home?

284
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:26,280
The Young Master has ordered

285
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,800
that no one leave

286
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:29,080
until the case is solved.

287
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:30,280
He's so young.

288
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,640
There's no way he's the killer.

289
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:32,520
Just let him go.

290
00:13:32,660 --> 00:13:33,440
If anything happens,

