00:25:27,220 --> 00:25:28,160
What's the matter?

581
00:25:28,820 --> 00:25:30,040
Why don't you ask your cousin?

582
00:25:32,080 --> 00:25:33,120
I don't know anything.

583
00:25:34,040 --> 00:25:34,680
I mean...

584
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:36,160
Magistrate Guo.

585
00:25:36,220 --> 00:25:37,440
Since it's your family matter,

586
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:38,880
I won't be in your way.

587
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,220
Excuse me, please.

588
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:50,600
What's going on?

589
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:52,680
See for yourself.

590
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:04,640
He Chun!

591
00:26:07,040 --> 00:26:07,440
Yes, sir?

592
00:26:08,380 --> 00:26:09,320
Check this for me.

593
00:26:19,360 --> 00:26:20,240
Bloodfang Toxin.

594
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:21,760
In mild cases,

595
00:26:21,760 --> 00:26:23,860
it causes stiff mouth and limbs,
similar to dementia.

596
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,380
In severe cases, it leads to coma.

597
00:26:30,800 --> 00:26:31,840
What's going on here?

598
00:26:34,040 --> 00:26:35,080
I don't know.

599
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:39,320
I really don't know.

600
00:26:39,600 --> 00:26:40,640
Where did you get this?

601
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:42,880
It was him.

602
00:26:43,280 --> 00:26:44,040
He...

603
00:26:44,280 --> 00:26:45,680
Who told you to poison me?

604
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:47,640
I don't know.

605
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:48,440
He clearly said...

606
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:49,200
Who is he?

607
00:26:51,520 --> 00:26:52,000
Ying.

608
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:54,920
Zilu?

609
00:26:56,520 --> 00:26:57,180
Come here.

610
00:27:07,020 --> 00:27:07,920
What's the matter?

611
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:10,040
You're in such a rush.

612
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:12,160
Are you going to see my younger brother?

613
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:16,840
Your devotion

614
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:19,240
is truly touching.

615
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:21,520
What's it to you?

616
00:27:26,600 --> 00:27:28,560
Don't get angry.

617
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:31,560
Everyone knows you're devoted to Zijie.

618
00:27:32,080 --> 00:27:33,080
But I'm worried

619
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:35,000
that your devotion

620
00:27:35,280 --> 00:27:36,720
might be misplaced.

621
00:27:39,360 --> 00:27:40,240
What do you mean?

622
00:27:40,560 --> 00:27:41,520
Explain it clearly.

623
00:27:42,120 --> 00:27:43,720
Why don't you still get it?

624
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:46,200
You're pure-hearted.

625
00:27:46,640 --> 00:27:47,600
But Cao Xuanxuan

626
00:27:47,800 --> 00:27:49,200
is malicious.

627
00:27:49,600 --> 00:27:51,000
You're alone out there.

628
00:27:51,060 --> 00:27:52,660
How could you possibly compete with her?

629
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:53,400
Don't you agree?

630
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:57,200
What should I do?

631
00:27:57,640 --> 00:27:59,120
I can help you.

632
00:27:59,840 --> 00:28:00,360
Dali.

633
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:07,880
What's this?

634
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:08,740
I don't want it.

635
00:28:11,360 --> 00:28:12,040
Ying,

636
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:13,240
listen to me.

637
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:14,920
This is Golden Azalea Extract.

638
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:16,120
If used on a person,

639
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:17,160
it causes rashes.

640
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:18,840
You see.

641
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:22,720
If Cao Xuanxuan breaks out in rashes,

642
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:24,960
Zijie will naturally
be disgusted with her.

643
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:28,400
Then what chance does she have
against you after that?

644
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:30,640
If you marry Zijie,

645
00:28:30,880 --> 00:28:32,000
the Guo and Liu families

646
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,920
will be even closer.

647
00:28:34,560 --> 00:28:36,040
What is Cao Xuanxuan?

648
00:28:37,120 --> 00:28:38,920
She's only an outsider.

649
00:28:40,760 --> 00:28:41,880
As your cousin,

650
00:28:42,320 --> 00:28:44,520
I will always stand by your side.

651
00:28:45,040 --> 00:28:45,680
But

652
00:28:46,120 --> 00:28:47,560
how you handle this

653
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:51,520
is still

654
00:28:51,680 --> 00:28:53,440
up to you.

655
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:58,240
Ying is not evil by nature.

656
00:28:58,340 --> 00:29:00,140
There must be some misunderstanding

657
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:02,600
for her to do something like this.

658
00:29:02,820 --> 00:29:03,820
Misunderstanding?

659
00:29:03,840 --> 00:29:05,140
How is this a misunderstanding

660
00:29:05,180 --> 00:29:06,440
when the evidence is concrete?

661
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:08,720
Xuanxuan.

662
00:29:10,360 --> 00:29:11,800
Once the Lyu Residence case is over,

663
00:29:12,120 --> 00:29:13,080
I will look into this.

664
00:29:13,360 --> 00:29:14,440
Is that alright?

665
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:15,480
Guo Zijie,

666
00:29:15,660 --> 00:29:16,680
I'll remember this.

667
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:17,640
Xuanxuan.

668
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:18,240
Don't touch me!

669
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:27,160
Zijie,

670
00:29:27,840 --> 00:29:28,800
I had no idea.

671
00:29:29,140 --> 00:29:30,340
Why don't you go back first?

672
00:29:51,840 --> 00:29:53,040
Something bad had happened!

673
00:29:54,280 --> 00:29:54,840
What is it?

674
00:29:55,240 --> 00:29:56,360
The Imperial Envoy is dead.

675
00:29:56,600 --> 00:29:57,480
He's dead?

676
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:34,480
The deceased shows no signs
of being dragged after death.

677
00:30:34,600 --> 00:30:36,160
This should be the first crime scene.

678
00:30:36,920 --> 00:30:38,280
The time of death

679
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:39,840
was around the hour of Chou.

680
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:42,560
There are no signs of a struggle.

681
00:30:42,800 --> 00:30:43,640
The fatal wound

682
00:30:43,720 --> 00:30:44,440
is on the back.

683
00:30:45,120 --> 00:30:46,320
The Chou hour again.

684
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:48,120
The door and windows were locked too.

685
00:30:49,360 --> 00:30:51,080
Another locked-room murder.

686
00:30:52,800 --> 00:30:53,440
Magistrate Guo,

687
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:56,920
who is committing

688
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:59,600
these crimes in my house?

689
00:31:00,520 --> 00:31:01,200
Calm down.

690
00:31:01,840 --> 00:31:03,440
The knife wound is on the back

691
00:31:03,560 --> 00:31:05,480
and no signs of a struggle beforehand.

692
00:31:06,000 --> 00:31:07,840
And from the angle of the stab,

693
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:10,360
the killer must have been very close
to Mr. Zhao at the time.

694
00:31:10,520 --> 00:31:12,320
But Mr. Zhao was caught off guard.

695
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:15,920
It shows

696
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:17,320
Mr. Zhao should know

697
00:31:18,120 --> 00:31:19,120
the killer.

698
00:31:19,980 --> 00:31:21,840
The only ones
who are familiar with Mr. Zhao

699
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:23,760
are me and a few of my friends.

700
00:31:24,040 --> 00:31:25,840
But we were all together last night.

701
00:31:26,060 --> 00:31:27,480
Besides, the others in the house

702
00:31:27,480 --> 00:31:29,480
don't know Mr. Zhao at all.

703
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,440
If they didn't know him,

704
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:34,000
it would be difficult
to kill him from behind

705
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,080
without him noticing.

706
00:31:42,440 --> 00:31:42,960
Xuanxuan,

707
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:44,100
what do you think?

708
00:31:44,680 --> 00:31:45,780
What else can I add

709
00:31:45,820 --> 00:31:46,860
when you've said it all?

710
00:31:51,760 --> 00:31:54,280
Luo Ji and Mr. Zhao have both died.

711
00:31:55,960 --> 00:31:57,840
I suspect the killer
might be the same person.

712
00:31:59,080 --> 00:32:01,160
But what is the connection
between these two?

713
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:04,240
Could there be

714
00:32:04,480 --> 00:32:06,440
something we've missed?

715
00:32:17,360 --> 00:32:18,160
What's wrong?

716
00:32:21,840 --> 00:32:22,440
Zijie,

717
00:32:22,960 --> 00:32:24,040
I think some things

718
00:32:24,360 --> 00:32:25,520
should be said in person.

719
00:32:26,580 --> 00:32:28,120
Xuanxuan is not an unreasonable person.

720
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,440
Just explain it to her.

721
00:32:34,760 --> 00:32:36,260
I don't know what to say to her.

722
00:32:36,980 --> 00:32:39,320
If you don't go,
it'll look like you're avoiding her.

723
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:41,520
Just go.

724
00:32:41,660 --> 00:32:42,580
Come on. Go. Hurry up.

725
00:32:43,040 --> 00:32:43,360
Go.

726
00:32:44,520 --> 00:32:45,120
Just go.

727
00:32:47,420 --> 00:32:48,880
Don't you know how to coax a woman?

728
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:51,360
Do you?

729
00:32:58,400 --> 00:32:59,360
What are you writing?

730
00:33:01,840 --> 00:33:02,760
I'm not telling you.

731
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:10,560
Xuanxuan,

732
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:13,320
do you want

733
00:33:14,520 --> 00:33:15,880
to hear my story?

734
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:20,280
What?

735
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:27,120
When I was young,

736
00:33:28,840 --> 00:33:30,400
I was close to Brother.

737
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:33,080
Later, my mother passed away.

738
00:33:34,420 --> 00:33:36,000
My father, after all, was a man.

739
00:33:37,160 --> 00:33:38,920
He only focused on our studies.

740
00:33:39,200 --> 00:33:40,840
My elder brother, with his bold nature,

741
00:33:41,120 --> 00:33:42,120
didn't like studying.

742
00:33:42,840 --> 00:33:44,680
So he would often be scolded by Father.

743
00:33:45,280 --> 00:33:46,520
Over time,

744
00:33:46,840 --> 00:33:48,600
he began to feel
that our father was biased.

745
00:33:49,240 --> 00:33:51,040
When the family secured
an official post,

746
00:33:51,360 --> 00:33:52,980
Father sent me instead of him.

747
00:33:53,240 --> 00:33:54,360
As the eldest son,

748
00:33:55,360 --> 00:33:56,440
Brother feared

749
00:33:56,800 --> 00:33:57,640
that one day

750
00:33:57,640 --> 00:33:58,640
I might replace him

751
00:33:59,560 --> 00:34:00,600
and take his inheritance.

752
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:05,560
So

753
00:34:07,520 --> 00:34:09,400
you're avoiding confrontation

754
00:34:09,720 --> 00:34:11,320
just to avoid competing with him?

755
00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:16,320
So what if you are?

756
00:34:16,600 --> 00:34:17,840
You brothers suspect each other.

757
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:18,960
He's afraid I might help you.

758
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:20,320
So he wants to poison me?

759
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:21,080
Why?

760
00:34:21,080 --> 00:34:22,160
What have I done wrong?

761
00:34:25,560 --> 00:34:26,200
Xuanxuan,

762
00:34:27,160 --> 00:34:27,880
trust me.

763
00:34:28,440 --> 00:34:29,440
After I return,

764
00:34:29,540 --> 00:34:31,440
I will definitely clear things up
with him.

765
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:36,520
What about Liu Ying?

766
00:34:37,040 --> 00:34:38,280
Why are you taking her side?

767
00:34:39,080 --> 00:34:40,400
When did I take her side?

768
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:42,520
She

769
00:34:42,720 --> 00:34:43,600
is open and honest.

770
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:45,480
She's probably been deceived by Brother.

771
00:34:46,120 --> 00:34:47,560
But since she did this,

772
00:34:47,720 --> 00:34:49,680
the Guo Residence
can no longer let her stay.

773
00:34:51,560 --> 00:34:52,640
After all, she's a woman.

774
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:55,040
If word of this gets out,

775
00:34:55,240 --> 00:34:56,680
her life is basically over.

776
00:34:57,160 --> 00:34:58,640
I only want to give her a way out.

777
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:05,840
You've been together for so long.

778
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,480
Don't you have any feelings for her?

779
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:09,400
I...

780
00:35:09,480 --> 00:35:10,200
I...

781
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:10,920
She and I...

782
00:35:10,920 --> 00:35:13,040
I haven't even spoken
a few words to her.

783
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:15,080
If it weren't for you

784
00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:16,080
who fell unconscious,

785
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:18,160
Father kept talking

786
00:35:18,240 --> 00:35:21,680
about how the greatest sin
is being unfilial,

787
00:35:21,800 --> 00:35:23,160
and having no heirs is the worst.

788
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:25,280
I really didn't want

789
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:26,640
to listen to him go on about it.

790
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:28,320
So I...

791
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:30,520
You understand, right?

792
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:36,680
You can leave.

793
00:35:36,680 --> 00:35:37,360
I get it now.

794
00:35:49,440 --> 00:35:50,040
Xuanxuan.

795
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:52,400
Xuanxuan?

796
00:35:57,240 --> 00:35:58,040
Don't be mad.

797
00:35:58,520 --> 00:35:58,960
All right?

798
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:12,960
Don't be mad,

799
00:36:13,200 --> 00:36:13,680
all right?

800
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:18,000
Guo Zijie.

801
00:36:19,480 --> 00:36:20,160
Why are you here?

802
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:21,240
You should go back.

803
00:36:21,240 --> 00:36:22,440
I'm still not done cooking.

804
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:24,240
I didn't know you knew how to cook.

805
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:26,320
My cooking is great.

806
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:30,520
Second Madam.

807
00:36:30,520 --> 00:36:31,640
Second Madam, be careful.

808
00:36:32,040 --> 00:36:32,960
Who's that?

809
00:36:33,200 --> 00:36:34,400
She's the Second Madam.

810
00:36:34,480 --> 00:36:35,400
She fell into a trance.

811
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:36,640
So she's not clear-headed.

812
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:37,880
I'll leave you two to your work.

813
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:38,940
I'll go and check on her.

814
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:41,280
Second Madam

815
00:36:41,640 --> 00:36:42,600
fell into a trance?

816
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:44,360
Could she

817
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:45,760
have been frightened by something?

818
00:36:46,980 --> 00:36:48,640
It looks like the killer is still here.

819
00:36:50,160 --> 00:36:51,240
Hurry up and head back now.

820
00:36:51,240 --> 00:36:51,920
I'm almost done.

821
00:36:51,960 --> 00:36:53,040
I'll send it over to you.

822
00:36:53,040 --> 00:36:53,820
Let me help you.

823
00:36:53,820 --> 00:36:55,120
I can crack an egg with one hand.

824
00:36:55,140 --> 00:36:56,080
I can do that too.

825
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,040
Just go back.

826
00:36:57,580 --> 00:36:58,000
Be good.

827
00:36:58,120 --> 00:36:58,480
Go.

828
00:37:12,120 --> 00:37:13,000
Miss Xuanxuan.

829
00:37:14,720 --> 00:37:15,360
Oh, Xiaolin.

830
00:37:16,560 --> 00:37:17,280
Why are you here?

831
00:37:19,680 --> 00:37:20,480
Miss Xuanxuan,

832
00:37:20,560 --> 00:37:21,600
why are you here?

833
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:23,560
Zijie went to prepare noodles

834
00:37:23,680 --> 00:37:24,360
for me.

835
00:37:25,300 --> 00:37:26,140
Please sit.

836
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:32,400
Uh...

837
00:37:32,520 --> 00:37:33,360
What's the matter?

838
00:37:33,720 --> 00:37:35,200
Is there anything you want to say?

839
00:37:36,720 --> 00:37:37,920
You should stay away

840
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:40,280
from Guo Zijie.

841
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:43,440
Why do you say so?

842
00:37:45,560 --> 00:37:46,560
Miss Xuanxuan,

843
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:48,640
you're my family's benefactor.

844
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:49,920
There are things

845
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:51,440
I didn't plan on telling.

846
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:53,400
But I saw you get along with him...

847
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:01,240
When you fell off the cliff,

848
00:38:01,960 --> 00:38:03,520
it was Guo Zijie's order.

849
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:09,120
Help!

850
00:38:55,241 --> 00:39:01,121
♪Like the setting sun,
which repeatedly sets in the west♪

851
00:39:02,381 --> 00:39:07,821
♪My heart goes over mountains
to rest with you♪

852
00:39:08,981 --> 00:39:12,421
♪As the winds and clouds shift,
our encounter♪

853
00:39:12,421 --> 00:39:16,181
♪Seems like the perfect foreshadowing♪

854
00:39:16,581 --> 00:39:21,621
♪But it was a misplaced expectation♪

855
00:39:23,141 --> 00:39:26,221
♪I think I'm exceptionally affectionate♪

856
00:39:26,421 --> 00:39:29,341
♪Devotion can warm the coldest ice♪

857
00:39:29,701 --> 00:39:32,901
♪And you're a shooting star
that flashes by♪

858
00:39:33,341 --> 00:39:35,621
♪Out of reach♪

859
00:39:36,701 --> 00:39:39,901
♪I prayed for a miracle countless times♪

860
00:39:40,181 --> 00:39:44,301
♪If I meet you, I only wish
we could be together forever♪

861
00:39:44,581 --> 00:39:50,701
♪But only the distant phantom remains♪

862
00:39:50,821 --> 00:39:53,861
♪Love rises like the wind
but remains unsettled when it stops♪

863
00:39:54,141 --> 00:39:57,141
♪Chasing you through four seasons,
wandering for a lifetime♪

864
00:39:57,421 --> 00:39:59,101
♪Fish in the water♪

865
00:39:59,101 --> 00:40:04,341
♪Is greedy for the reflection
